          "latency_ms": 14508,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "In 2024, the Offlimits helpline received a record number of 12,206 contacts related to online transgressive behaviours. Many of these requests for help relate to harmful content or contact that, while not necessarily illegal, often result from poor platform design or the absence of adequate regulation, facilitating harmful behaviours. Offlimits believes it is important to have a fair digital design, particularly for children, whose developing cognitive and emotional capacities make them especially vulnerable to manipulation and exploitation.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s0",
          "section_path": [],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
          "chunk_word_count": 78,
          "char_len": 547
        }
      },
      {
        "para_id": "p10",
        "items": [],
        "meta": {
          "skipped": false,
          "skip_reason": null,
          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 4496,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Therefore, Offlimits supports the development of a Digital Fairness Act. We would like to highlight a few areas of concern:",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s0",
          "section_path": [],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
          "chunk_word_count": 20,
          "char_len": 123
        }
